  "detailed_description": "<strong>Brutal Wizardry</strong> is a magic shooter with procedural level generation in virtual reality. You will fight against hordes of dark fantasy enemies using magic wands that will shoot fireballs, lightning and other magic. Earn gold, get new weapons and learn perks. Move to choose the most advantageous position, activate mechanisms and traps to destroy your enemies. Protect yourself with a shield. Learn the mechanics and interact with dynamic objects to destroy creatures most efficiently.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR-Exclusive Mechanics</h2>Telekinesis, bow, shields<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/082ed205f68bb855a44bf0bb0be5e8b7.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/082ed205f68bb855a44bf0bb0be5e8b7.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/082ed205f68bb855a44bf0bb0be5e8b7.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Magic</h2>Various<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/e6c8faded102f4d5b1fb07aacf854764.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/e6c8faded102f4d5b1fb07aacf854764.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/e6c8faded102f4d5b1fb07aacf854764.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanisms and Traps</h2>Combine with telekinesis<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/fc448ed9295e10e2738cbbfc5d856f96.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/fc448ed9295e10e2738cbbfc5d856f96.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/fc448ed9295e10e2738cbbfc5d856f96.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Lot of Magic Weapons</h2>8 wands and 10 additional weapons - shields and other stuff<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/ec38d36610850159a4acc3670c59d395.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/ec38d36610850159a4acc3670c59d395.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/ec38d36610850159a4acc3670c59d395.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Randomly Generated Arenas</h2>Due to procedural generation, each new level will be different from the previous one. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/bc7899e1dee3f66edc47f9d319e4435e.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/bc7899e1dee3f66edc47f9d319e4435e.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/bc7899e1dee3f66edc47f9d319e4435e.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Movement Options and Interaction</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>teleportation and/or smoooth locomotion<br></li><li>snap turn and smooth rotation<br></li><li>Left/right primary hand</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Brutal Wizardry</strong> is a magic shooter with procedural level generation in virtual reality. You will fight against hordes of dark fantasy enemies using magic wands that will shoot fireballs, lightning and other magic. Earn gold, get new weapons and learn perks. Move to choose the most advantageous position, activate mechanisms and traps to destroy your enemies. Protect yourself with a shield. Learn the mechanics and interact with dynamic objects to destroy creatures most efficiently.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR-Exclusive Mechanics</h2>Telekinesis, bow, shields<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/082ed205f68bb855a44bf0bb0be5e8b7.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/082ed205f68bb855a44bf0bb0be5e8b7.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/082ed205f68bb855a44bf0bb0be5e8b7.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Magic</h2>Various<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/e6c8faded102f4d5b1fb07aacf854764.poster.avif?t=1725000188\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/e6c8faded102f4d5b1fb07aacf854764.webm?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416820/extras/e6c8faded102f4d5b1fb07aacf854764.mp4?t=1725000188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mechanisms and Traps</h2>Combine with telekinesis<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb